text: The 1993 Humo European Open was a professional ranking snooker tournament that took place in February 1993 at the Arenahal in Antwerp, Belgium. Only the latter stages, from the last-16, were played in Antwerp. Steve Davis won the tournament, defeating Stephen Hendry 10–4 in the final. __TOC__ ==Main draw== ==References== Category:European Masters (snooker) European Open European Open European Open Category:Snooker in Belgium Category:Sports competitions in Antwerp
